Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.68,English,,0,0,0,,And that's unique in human history, okay?\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.08,English,,0,0,0,,We say Shakespeare was a great writer and\N{\rChinese}...
