Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.06,0:50:06.52,English,,0,0,0,,Homer created the capacity for empathy and imagination.\N{\rChinese}荷马创作了同感与想象的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.14,0:50:11.02,English,,0,0,0,,The playwright created the capacity for inner debate and perspective.\N{\rChinese}剧作家创作了内在辩论与视角的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.78,0:50:15.46,English,,0,0,0,,The philosophers created the capacity for reason and reflection.\N{\rChinese}哲学家们创造了理想与思考的能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.36,0:50:19.22,English,,0,0,0,,You now have a new human mind.\N{\rChinese}现在给你一个新的人类思维。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.54,0:50:24.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And when you study all of them.\N{\rChinese}好的，回到本身。”
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.86,0:50:28.18,English,,0,0,0,,This is what we call a liberal arts education.\N{\rChinese}这就是我们所说的自由艺术教育。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.04,0:50:32.12,English,,0,0,0,,Alright? And guess what?\N{\rChinese}好，回到本身？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.68,0:50:38.18,English,,0,0,0,,Our greatest thinkers came to us through the liberal arts.\N{\rChinese}我们的最优秀的古典文学…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.30,0:50:40.24,English,,0,0,0,,Alright? Alright? Alright?\N{\rChinese}好的？好的？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.24,0:50:42.14,English,,0,0,0,,Alright? Alright?\N{\rChinese}好的？好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.32,0:50:47.92,English,,0,0,0,,the greatest thinkers of the past 20 years,\N{\rChinese}好的，...??
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.50,0:50:52.48,English,,0,0,0,,they all, what was common about them is, they all read the Greeks.\N{\rChinese}他们都一样，什么是共同点就是他们都读了希腊的文字。
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.22,0:50:54.48,English,,0,0,0,,And that was just their education.\N{\rChinese}又是个别的……………??
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.84,0:51:00.28,English,,0,0,0,,Alright, so this is the first legacy of the Greeks.\N{\rChinese}先前……??
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.42,0:51:03.26,English,,0,0,0,,A new way of being and seeing.\N{\rChinese}一个新的存在与观照方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.46,0:51:11.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? Second thing is,\N{\rChinese}OK? 这算是个别的??
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.88,0:51:15.30,English,,0,0,0,,now that you have this Greek world,\N{\rChinese}??
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.42,0:51:21.62,English,,0,0,0,,the Greeks need to establish a cohesive cultural identity.\N{\rChinese}希腊人需要建立统一的文化身份。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.52,0:51:24.12,English,,0,0,0,,And they did that\N{\rChinese}他们做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.12,0:51:27.44,English,,0,0,0,,by promoting a Greek education.\N{\rChinese}通过推广希腊教育。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.74,0:51:30.96,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, but not only that, but\N{\rChinese}??
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.96,0:51:33.88,English,,0,0,0,,they had to bring in local people into this education.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.52,0:51:37.72,English,,0,0,0,,So one major function of the Library of Alexandria\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.26,0:51:40.96,English,,0,0,0,,was to standardize and systemize Greek knowledge.\N{\rChinese}为了统一并系统化希腊知识。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.18,0:51:44.40,English,,0,0,0,,And they did this by standardizing the text.\N{\rChinese}他们通过统一文本来完成此事。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.58,0:51:46.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so there are different texts that were written by Homer.\N{\rChinese}好的，...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.74,0:51:48.90,English,,0,0,0,,The text of Homer that\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.90,0:51:52.64,English,,0,0,0,,we have today was developed by the people at the Library of Alexandria.\N{\rChinese}我们今天所拥有的，正是由亚历山大图书馆的人们所发展出来的。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.06,0:51:57.10,English,,0,0,0,,Standardization. They also did something called commentaries.\N{\rChinese}标准化。它们还做了一个叫做“注释”。”
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.22,0:51:59.94,English,,0,0,0,,So commentaries are basically like teacher handbooks.\N{\rChinese}注释基本上是教师手册的样子。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.10,0:52:02.64,English,,0,0,0,,They teach you how to teach this stuff.\N{\rChinese}它们给你们说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.62,0:52:06.12,English,,0,0,0,,And they create like footnotes and\N{\rChinese}译文1
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.12,0:52:08.64,English,,0,0,0,,chapters and page numbers,\N{\rChinese}译文2
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.18,0:52:11.00,English,,0,0,0,,codices, indexes.\N{\rChinese}译文
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.14,0:52:15.84,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the point was to make Greek education\N{\rChinese}]? ?????????????????????????? ...?????? ...?????? ...??? ...??? ...??..?????? ...??..??? “………”……………………………………………………?……..??………………………?……..??………
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.32,0:52:18.98,English,,0,0,0,,available and accessible to anyone.\N{\rChinese}可用且可接触的…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.84,0:52:24.48,English,,0,0,0,,All right, and what this means is, we in China now can actually read Homer,\N{\rChinese}翻译后...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.34,0:52:27.26,English,,0,0,0,,Issylus, and Plato for ourselves.\N{\rChinese}\}]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.52,0:52:29.44,English,,0,0,0,,Even though we are not culturally Greek.\N{\rChinese}Even though we are not culturally Greek.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.98,0:52:34.40,English,,0,0,0,,And that's the benefit of the pan -Hellenistic project.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.92,0:52:38.36,English,,0,0,0,,All right. And\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.36,0:52:40.38,English,,0,0,0,,the third major benefit\N{\rChinese}第三个主要好处
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.38,0:52:46.30,English,,0,0,0,,is Greek knowledge meant a global development.\N{\rChinese}是希腓知识成了全球发展。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.30,0:52:50.28,English,,0,0,0,,Revolution. And innovation, okay?\N{\rChinese}翻译1
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.42,0:52:52.86,English,,0,0,0,,And what I mean by that is, remember,\N{\rChinese}翻译2
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.14,0:52:56.54,English,,0,0,0,,Greek knowledge is being spread all around the world.\N{\rChinese}希腓知识正在全球传播。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.72,0:53:00.08,English,,0,0,0,,And then they're interacting with powerful local cultures.\N{\rChinese}随后它们与当地强大文化相互作用。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.04,0:53:03.56,English,,0,0,0,,And through the process of synchronization,\N{\rChinese}通过同步过程，新的知识形态正在形成。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.06,0:53:07.06,English,,0,0,0,,new forms of knowledge are being created.\N{\rChinese}通过同步过程，新型知识形态正在生成。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.82,0:53:09.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？所以
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.46,0:53:12.64,English,,0,0,0,,the Greeks spread the knowledge to India.\N{\rChinese}希腓的知识在古希腓里传到古印度
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.84,0:53:16.28,English,,0,0,0,,And now it's interacting with local Indian philosophies.\N{\rChinese}现在它与当地印度哲学相互作用。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.30,0:53:18.90,English,,0,0,0,,And religion, including new ideas.\N{\rChinese}宗教与新思想相互作用。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.32,0:53:20.82,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So\N{\rChinese}好的？所以
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.82,0:53:23.64,English,,0,0,0,,the most famous synchronization\N{\rChinese}最 先前的同步化
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.64,0:53:27.06,English,,0,0,0,,is in the Levant.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.18,0:53:30.68,English,,0,0,0,,Greek knowledge was being spread to the Jews.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.98,0:53:35.32,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And so when you put the Greeks and the Jews together,\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.76,0:53:39.56,English,,0,0,0,,you have a new idea that\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.56,0:53:41.90,English,,0,0,0,,would forever revolutionize human history.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.04,0:53:44.70,English,,0,0,0,,And it's called Christianity. All right?\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.70,0:53:47.42,English,,0,0,0,,So Christianity would not have been possible if it\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.42,0:53:51.02,English,,0,0,0,,were not for the work of Aristotle.\N{\rChinese}未必为亚里士多德的工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.70,0:53:54.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right.\N{\rChinese}好的？好吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.78,0:53:58.08,English,,0,0,0,,So those are the three major legacies of the Greeks.\N{\rChinese}于是这就是希腊的三大遗产。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.38,0:53:59.50,English,,0,0,0,,And so it is,\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.60,0:54:04.58,English,,0,0,0,,I think it's perfectly fair to say the Greeks were the most influential\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:06.86,English,,0,0,0,,and consequential civilization of all time.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.20,0:54:12.02,English,,0,0,0,,They were certainly the most creative. No other civilization even comes close to their creativity.\N{\rChinese}他们确实是最具创造力的。没有其他文明能与之相提并论。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.12,0:54:16.82,English,,0,0,0,,All right? Okay.\N{\rChinese}好吧？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.90,0:54:20.08,English,,0,0,0,,So that's it. Any questions?\N{\rChinese}于是就是这样。还有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.90,0:54:24.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So…\N{\rChinese}好的，...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.40,0:54:28.68,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So we are finished with the Greeks.\N{\rChinese}好的，...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.80,0:54:32.06,English,,0,0,0,,Next class we start a new unit on Rome…\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.06,0:54:33.96,English,,0,0,0,,Roman history. All right?\N{\rChinese}罗马史。好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.02,0:54:36.50,English,,0,0,0,,So… Great.\N{\rChinese}好，...太好了。
